{"tid":1560483,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"占831太子站警方有冇打死人","createTime":"2019-09-11T08:15:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T03:01:18.000Z","uid":178205,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fe101c5bcb0dea1f6c44cc9149542cc66463c0c3","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"純屬易理研討 百無禁忌<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97BgKxr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97BgKxr.jpg&h=4cd745f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇落無，有損傷而無死"},{"pid":"9c292dc8e1a1e83b653c53847f0a463269d3e60c","tid":1560483,"uid":316569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"解釋一下"},{"pid":"b6fc041ba904aae123491b39e8f824b1650288ee","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9c292dc8e1a1e83b653c53847f0a463269d3e60c","tid":1560483,"uid":316569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T08:30:34.000Z","msg":"解釋一下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"官鬼popo，子孫為示威者(反官之人)為用<br />\n<br />\n亥水子孫月生，臨日 極旺，無死象<br />\n<br />\n父母丑土動克，父母為建制藍絲，俾佢哋打<br />\n<br />\n二爻妻財卯木動而空，不能制，所以受災<br />\n<br />\n又空而且破，反而普通市民受傷最大。<br />\n<br />\n兌為損傷，毀折，上下兌，兩者爭鬥，下卦動，平民損傷。<br />\n<br />\n但係因為發生時間重點係過咗11點，我再占一卦，睇下9月1日(過子時情況係點)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2RHGoL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2RHGoL.jpg&h=7d3ebc4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下卦會財局克父，卯木空破，但有氣不死<br />\n<br />\n官鬼靜。<br />\n<br />\n六三，眾允，悔亡。有團結，不再擔憂嘅意思。<br />\n<br />\n會局亦有團結之意<br />\n<br />\n化六沖離卦，有離或者戰的意思。離為羅，亦有捕捉之意<br />\n<br />\n純粹睇卦 我對831詳情唔太了解，又冇得睇CCTV<br />\n<br />\n有平民受傷，走甩咗，想封站捉人，咁一係就捉唔到，一係就捉到，但係太柒，關公危機，所以唔想俾人知。"},{"pid":"411774ff618d3c41ca946f72b7f0dfcac94206d1","tid":1560483,"uid":177150,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T17:57:35.000Z","msg":"blk 完"},{"pid":"7ed6651dfec1ca223f6525ad7008f1c0f26cdbb5","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:48:09.000Z","msg":"補充，如果真係有咩事，係隱瞞咗，一個禮拜之內，會爆出嚟。出空之故。"},{"pid":"560f088ff6ae2a4a2c1659dfd30c854c9c4682a2","tid":1560483,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed6651dfec1ca223f6525ad7008f1c0f26cdbb5","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:48:09.000Z","msg":"補充，如果真係有咩事，係隱瞞咗，一個禮拜之內，會爆出嚟。出空之故。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:52:59.000Z","msg":"黎緊一星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇得占埋新屋嶺強姦殺人係咪真有其事"},{"pid":"83a696dc3c9a8b9274afb852b017a98dc88c5d16","tid":1560483,"uid":271894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ed6651dfec1ca223f6525ad7008f1c0f26cdbb5","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:48:09.000Z","msg":"補充，如果真係有咩事，係隱瞞咗，一個禮拜之內，會爆出嚟。出空之故。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T21:54:41.000Z","msg":"黎緊一星期？"},{"pid":"32d776d538bcb5538452e4fba3b1345229ff623b","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:02:59.000Z","msg":"係嚟緊一星期。<br />\n占新屋嶺係可以，但係算啦，我能力唔夠 搵啲叻啲嘅做<br />\n以前啲人成日話洩漏天機會被天罰<br />\n其實就係太大件事，講乜都有人唔鍾意，係被人罰。<br />\n占到有冇又如何，都係得個廢噏。<br />\n呢支卦都當我鳩噏啦，不嬲都唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0ffc9f979fb072b2c6b3a935233f7f9b3804f8e","tid":1560483,"uid":189781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T22:08:33.000Z","msg":"喂<br />\n<br />\n你出得post 又咁無信心<br />\n<br />\n咁你不如不占啦<br />\n<br />\n心誠則靈<br />\n<br />\n既然唔信既，你何必占呢"},{"pid":"829ce6af2a501f8fec6e43121693868b3b65ed23","tid":1560483,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T23:00:21.000Z","msg":"901凌晨先死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daefa1709db0ee3e07a85fe92d110cefc803775f","tid":1560483,"uid":178205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo